org.talend.sdk.component.api.input

Annotation Type Emitter


  • @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Emitter
    Mark a class as returning an input connector. This is only useful when there is no PartitionMapper.
